caption.p: AG-ME induced loss of MMP and caspase enzyme activities in MCF-7 cells. (a) Representative images showing MMP level by Rh-123 probe in control and 1000 μg/ml of AG-ME. (b) Quantification of intensity of Rh-123 dye in MCF-7 cells treated with AG-ME at 250-1000 μg/ml. (c) Caspase-3 and (d) caspase-9 enzyme activities. ∗ p < 0.05 and ∗∗ p < 0.01 vs. the control.
